{"tid":1422133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然好想知  係我地人多 定d 監獄床位數量","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:58:33.000Z","uid":289235,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0350eefc96ec2b49257b16e3b31cddf90ea17d","tid":1422133,"uid":289235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"如果我地迫爆咗佢，咁會點！！"},{"pid":"29b50e52c66d02571e9afd6d5b872dfd57d459e3","tid":1422133,"uid":292938,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"香港本身咪就係監獄囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299ca5d21cf00d97036db3aba3feff2127afb442","tid":1422133,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"劏左監獄佢"},{"pid":"8cd8074fbb1007eb2c8f9745dbbd0c9193a4fb29","tid":1422133,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb0350eefc96ec2b49257b16e3b31cddf90ea17d","tid":1422133,"uid":289235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:03.000Z","msg":"如果我地迫爆咗佢，咁會點！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:55:58.000Z","msg":"會係大陸整集中營"},{"pid":"d212ae8b97433718dcf1925344461363801a0388","tid":1422133,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"[懶人包]黑警記者會重點及拆招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4522167c6642af12519cf1686ccde141e3e0ddf1","tid":1422133,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:57:46.000Z","msg":"監獄床位都大過出面劏房<br />\n<br />\n據政府統計處2015年的調查，本港近20萬人居於8.88萬個劏房，人均居住面積僅62.4平方呎，比一個75平方呎的獨立囚倉還小。無論勞碌大半輩子的老人家，還是正值成長階段的小朋友，都難逃蝸居斗室之苦。<br />\n<br />\n劏房蟻族渴望上樓，若淪為公屋擠迫戶，也不見得比住劏房更寬敞。運輸及房屋局的資料顯示，目前仍有近10萬名公屋居民的人均居住面積，低於規定的75平方呎，當中更有1.7萬人的人均居住面積少於60平方呎，比劏房戶的情況更惡劣。"},{"pid":"88c6d18fb51b5e1d4de9b236f6b9bcf537c98ac5","tid":1422133,"uid":143621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"送你返去上面集中營咪得<br />\n<br />\n唔係以為有得係香港坐啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地一失敗 對家一定誅死我地 分分鐘拉去打把<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 必定要成功爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f297900ae59540fdf5becd0888d51465c389b73f","tid":1422133,"uid":289235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"299ca5d21cf00d97036db3aba3feff2127afb442","tid":1422133,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"劏左監獄佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係喎 香港一大特色 劏房"},{"pid":"269c51ea87f8c1992b1d4c283b4d6730b3de5e74","tid":1422133,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"律政司：我揀人告囉"}]}